      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Football or polo?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“足球还是水球？”。先抓住这个 title joke：这不是体育规则课，也不是让你区分 football 和 real water polo。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 13.734,
      "end": 27.174,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文里，孩子们在河岸上玩球，球却飞向河上的小船。足球从 land 飞到 water scene，所以题目开玩笑地问：这是 football，还是变成了 water-side polo？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 27.524,
      "end": 38.675,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先把空间摆清楚。这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "bank"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是 money bank，不是银行，而是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "river bank"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，河岸，也就是河边的土地。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 39.025,
      "end": 55.117,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "一张小地图就是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "river"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，旁边是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "bank"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "；children 在 bank 上玩球；people 在 river 上"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "rowing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，划小船；ball 从 bank 飞向 a passing boat。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 55.466,
      "end": 64.554,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The Wayle"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是这条小河的名字。你不用查它是不是很有名，只要记住：The Wayle 是主人公家附近的小河。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 64.904,
      "end": 76.824,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以这课的核心不是危险事故，而是一个轻轻的公园小插曲：quiet riverside afternoon，sudden flying ball，and a good-humoured man who throws the ball back."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 77.174,
      "end": 90.222,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "故事先给我们地点："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The Wayle is a small river that cuts across the park near my home."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "cuts across"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是横穿、穿过，像一条小河从公园中间经过。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 90.572,
      "end": 101.468,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "主人公喜欢这里："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I like sitting by the Wayle on fine afternoons."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "fine afternoons"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是天气好、适合坐在外面的下午。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 101.817,
      "end": 116.273,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "上星期日很暖和，所以他"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "went and sat on the river bank as usual"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。注意"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "as usual"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，像往常一样；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "river bank"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是河岸，不是银行。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 116.623,
      "end": 124.423,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "接着画面变热闹："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Some children were playing games on the bank"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。孩子们在岸上的草地玩游戏。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 124.772,
      "end": 134.308,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "同时，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "there were some people rowing on the river"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "row"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是用桨划小船，不是 motorboat，也不是大船。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 134.658,
      "end": 144.378,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里一定要看出两个 activity zones：on the bank 是陆地上，on the river 是河面上。大家共享同一个公园空间。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 144.728,
      "end": 152.736,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "突然事情来了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "One of the children kicked a ball very hard."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "一个孩子很用力地踢了一脚球。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 153.086,
      "end": 164.877,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "球的路线是关键："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It went towards a passing boat."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "towards"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是朝着某个方向；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "passing boat"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是正经过的小船。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 165.227,
      "end": 175.827,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "岸上的人看见了，就"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "called out to the man in the boat"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，大声提醒船上的人。可是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "he did not hear them"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，他没有听见。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 176.177,
      "end": 189.512,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后出现整课最重要的句型："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The ball struck him so hard that he nearly fell into the water."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "so hard that..."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“这么重，以至于……”，hit 的结果是 he nearly fell."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 189.862,
      "end": 202.566,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "主人公转头看孩子们："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I turned to look at the children, but there weren't any in sight."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "in sight"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是看得见；not in sight 就是一个也看不见。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 202.916,
      "end": 213.688,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么看不见？"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "They had all run away!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里用"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had run away"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，说明在主人公回头看之前，孩子们已经跑掉了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 214.038,
      "end": 223.197,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后不是生气，而是一个 warm ending："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The man laughed when he realized what had happened."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他明白发生了什么以后笑了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 223.547,
      "end": 234.031,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "called out to the children and threw the ball back to the bank"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。球从 bank 飞到 boat，又被 thrown back to the bank，标题的玩笑也就完整了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 234.381,
      "end": 238.165,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课为什么叫"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Football or polo?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "？"
        }
