      "end": 252.196,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。不是在认真讲 water polo 规则，而是一个 playful title。football 本来在岸上，结果进入了 river-and-boat scene。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
